item.description:
Hey Guys -

Let's take a little road trip down to The Rock Club in New Rochelle for some different climbs and fun!

I figure we can meet at CT Rock Gym at about 5:30 / 6:00 and then just carpool down there. It's only about 1 hr. away, and they're open until 10:30pm - so that will give us plenty of time to climb.

For more information on their gym, check out http://climbrockclub..... It's a pretty cool place and I'm looking forward to getting down their again!

If you're coming from points south of New Haven, then you could just meet us down there if you like.

Hope you all can come - let me know early so I can help to get rides for everyone.

As always, e-mail me if you have any questions.

-dan
item.name: New Rochelle Climbing Gym Road Trip
